data.description: Unlock the potential of this hidden gem! This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is a canvas waiting for your creativity. Experience the functionality of this open-concept living space. With an abundance of natural light, the living room, dining area, and kitchen create a spacious atmosphere that is ideal for entertaining. Seize the chance to add a special blend of your individual style and personality to every bedroom. Downstairs, the basement can serve as a laundry room, home office, retreat, and many other uses. Step outside to explore the wonderful backyard, a haven for summertime get-togethers and outdoor activities. For storage and off-street parking, there is a sizable garage on the property as well.
